## What is ours

The ~328k **derived** forms — the second pass that propagates an attested lemma stress across its
paradigm, the four constraints that keep it honest, and the learned blacklist in
`data/derivation-blocked.json` — are our work, and are offered under the same terms as the file
they live in. So is the front-coded file format. See `docs/ARCHITECTURE.md`.
